{"tid":1824354,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共黨校校刊載文  盛讚習近平貴族氣質","createTime":"2020-01-14T11:17:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-15T12:28:08.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"9305fa7d697fc5fc40fff2eef3eed21c2cf374dd","tid":1824354,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:17:40.000Z","msg":"中共中央黨校『學習時報』日前發文稱讚習近平&ldquo;平民情懷，貴族氣質&rdquo;，引發自媒體爆炸。&ldquo;跪族&rdquo;、&ldquo;喲，有一位最後的貴族哎!&rdquo; 各種驚嘆比比皆是。<br />\n<br />\n此文是以中央黨校校刊『學習時報』採訪習近平當年任職福建時的一位老部下林彬之口&ldquo;見證&rdquo;的：<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;近平同志的貴族氣質，是骨子裡透出來的。他講話沉穩而有哲理，語言平實，卻能深入人心；他走在大堂上，有一種氣定神閑、不言自威的風采。無論是和英國女王乘坐皇家馬車，還是和美國總統奧巴馬、特朗普在一起會談，他的氣場都足以鎮得住場、壓得住陣。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n這篇表明2017年6月3日的採訪，不知為何在元月10日才爆出來？翌日便是台灣總統大選，北京比較囑意的國民黨候選人韓國瑜被打敗，被視為台獨分子的民進黨蔡英文大勝連任。<br />\n<br />\n有網民問，&ldquo;難道坐了一趟英國女王的馬車，沒有害怕，就算具備貴族氣質了？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n還有網民問：&rdquo;把習主席說成貴族，這是公開說中國是封建帝制？這是給習主席抹黑吧？&ldquo;<br />\n<br />\n還有人記得習近平當年做王儲，擔任國家副主席訪問墨西哥說過的那幾句流傳很廣的話，&ldquo;有些吃飽了沒事幹的外國人，對我們的事情指手畫腳。中國一不輸出革命，二不輸出饑餓和貧困，三不去折騰你們，還有什麼好說的。&rdquo;&ldquo;吃飽了沒事幹&rdquo;從此成了一句習氏名言。這話當時就被嘲笑&ldquo;土得掉了渣&rdquo;，不過還算&ldquo;樸實&rdquo;，但硬要套上&ldquo;貴族氣質&rdquo;，不太合適。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200113-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E9%BB%A8%E6%A0%A1%E6%A0%A1%E5%88%8A%E8%BC%89%E6%96%87%E7%9B%9B%E8%AE%9A%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E8%B2%B4%E6%97%8F%E6%B0%A3%E8%B3%AA%E5%BC%95%E7%88%86%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20200113-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E6%25A0%25A1%25E5%2588%258A%25E8%25BC%2589%25E6%2596%2587%25E7%259B%259B%25E8%25AE%259A%25E7%25BF%2592%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E6%2597%258F%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E5%25BC%2595%25E7%2588%2586%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E7%25B5%25A1&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSert6RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=927760ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20200113-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E9%BB%A8%E6%A0%A1%E6%A0%A1%E5%88%8A%E8%BC%89%E6%96%87%E7%9B%9B%E8%AE%9A%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E8%B2%B4%E6%97%8F%E6%B0%A3%E8%B3%AA%E5%BC%95%E7%88%86%E7%B6%B2%E7%B5%A1</a>"},{"pid":"f899398ed4bd34e9a10cad8038e7ca4c5bc50ee7","tid":1824354,"uid":259519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:21:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">想救連登，試下依個方法</span><br />\n<br />\n【測試】熱門新功能&mdash;行動篇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1824310\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1824310</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"21d94f63f742d5e4894acd64a7f38075f6bc8ef1","tid":1824354,"uid":34189,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:22:48.000Z","msg":"單人匹馬鎮住6個俄佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1830000/1834021/111111111111_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1830000%2F1834021%2F111111111111_600.png&h=5f635a2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9dc0ca6fa6b8be98dad3fd806891370a2e503c3c","tid":1824354,"uid":280153,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"21d94f63f742d5e4894acd64a7f38075f6bc8ef1","tid":1824354,"uid":34189,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:22:48.000Z","msg":"單人匹馬鎮住6個俄佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1830000/1834021/111111111111_600.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1830000%2F1834021%2F111111111111_600.png&h=5f635a2d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T11:26:42.000Z","msg":"俄佬：嘩，你睇佢真人幾撚肥<br />\n<br />\n動物園睇禽獸咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9bef25a9fd36288d1abdad16aeaa6ff52b51308","tid":1824354,"uid":256077,"li